agazine for sharing knowledge in the Umbraco community.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-01-15T11:13:18.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Community</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/umbracoffee\">umbraCoffee</a> - a weekly YouTube series discussing recent Umbraco news.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-01-15T11:13:18.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Community</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLG_nqaT-rbpwZDRQmlfzslbJ-4UjgDcw0\">Unicorner</a> - YouTube series from the Chief Unicorn, Niels Hartvig.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-01-15T11:12:15.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Community</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://h5yr.com/\">#h5yr</a> - High Five, You Rock!</li>","updatedAt":"2019-01-15T11:11:52.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Backoffice extensions</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://our.umbraco.org/projects/developer-tools/robotstxt-editor\">Robots.txt editor</a> - Edit robots.txt from within the back-office.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-01-15T11:07:09.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Backoffice extensions</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://our.umbraco.org/projects/developer-tools/ui-o-matic/\">UI-O-Matic</a> - Auto generate an integrated crud UI in Umbraco for a db table based on a petapoco poco.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-01-15T11:07:09.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Backoffice extensions</h2><h3>Form Builders</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://umbraco.com/products/umbraco-forms/\">Umbraco Forms*</a> - The new Contour, use this to add forms to your site. <strong>(Developed by Umbraco HQ)</strong></li>","updatedAt":"2019-01-15T11:07:09.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Backoffice extensions</h2><h3>Property Editors</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://our.umbraco.org/projects/website-utilities/meganav/\">Meganav</a> - A flexible, draggable link picker for constructing site navigation menus, big or small.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-01-15T11:07:09.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Backoffice extensions</h2><h3>Property Editors</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=