","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://our.umbraco.org/projects/backoffice-extensions/nexu\">Nexu</a> - Keeps tracks of internal links by parsing property data. Will warn editors when something is \"in use\" when deleting or unpublishing. It's extensible so you can create parsers for your own property or grid editors.</li>","updatedAt":"2017-04-13T21:00:26.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Backoffice extensions</h2><h3>Property Editors</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://our.umbraco.org/projects/backoffice-extensions/terratype/\">Terratype</a> - A fully featured maps data type  supporting multiple map providers (Google Maps, Bing, Leaflet).</li>","updatedAt":"2017-04-13T19:34:56.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Backoffice extensions</h2><h3>Form Builders</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://our.umbraco.org/projects/backoffice-extensions/formulate/\">Formulate</a> - Build website forms (contact forms, newsletter sign ups, surveys, job applications) with no coding.</li>","updatedAt":"2017-04-13T18:06:16.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Backoffice extensions</h2><h3>Grid Editors</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://our.umbraco.org/projects/backoffice-extensions/doc-type-grid-editor/\">Doc Type Grid Editor</a> - Advanced grid editor for Umbraco.</li>","updatedAt":"2017-04-13T18:06:16.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Backoffice extensions</h2><h3>Property Editors</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://our.umbraco.org/projects/backoffice-extensions/skybrudimagepicker/\">Skybrud.ImagePicker</a> - a configurable image picker that can be used as either a property editor or grid editor. Each image can be supplemented with a title, description and/or link.</li>","updatedAt":"2017-04-13T18:06:16.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Backoffice extensions</h2><h3>Property Editors</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://our.umbraco.org/projects/backoffice-extensions/switcher/\">Switcher</a> - A simple property editor that works as an alternative to the core true/false datatype.</li>","updatedAt":"2017-